{"tid":2256174,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖]有冇人細細個差啲碌落樓梯？","createTime":"2020-10-24T06:59:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T15:48:43.000Z","uid":10337,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"4f7db8e93851bef6b3890a07c7872d3891d45512","tid":2256174,"uid":10337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T06:59:03.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n記得以前唔知小二定小三<br />\n個書包勁重勁大個<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有次趕時間搭電梯行落去<br />\n個書包重得滯 個人要向前傾先行到<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知傾得太前 個書包扯左我個人出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後好好彩 跳左2次幾級樓梯<br />\n雙腳落地 冇水花<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/handup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n示意圖：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GpuQwED.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGpuQwED.jpg&h=e3a075d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又有一次落樓梯又係書包太重同傾得太前<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果行到一最後唔知幾多級失平衡 凌空打咗個關斗<br />\n好彩係個書包落地<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Nd2nNY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Nd2nNY.jpg&h=ec492d10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人冇類似經歷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb475a68b11bb425a269e8fc25b08871d3aa36eb","tid":2256174,"uid":296551,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T07:02:21.000Z","msg":"書包係咪幾噸重？"},{"pid":"b55201befe326360fcc7c0095afdd2331e1b73ea","tid":2256174,"uid":10337,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"bb475a68b11bb425a269e8fc25b08871d3aa36eb","tid":2256174,"uid":296551,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T07:02:21.000Z","msg":"書包係咪幾噸重？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T07:04:41.000Z","msg":"冇磅過啦<br />\n但記得企直個人 好易向後反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e05ca4b8e2adf69119daa5440851a4e6dc0bd6b0","tid":2256174,"uid":50041,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T07:05:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20201020/__2020102019234392773.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20201020%2F__2020102019234392773.mp4&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLKf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=f924d5c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20201020%2F__2020102019234392773.mp4&h=eda4b4f9\" target=\"_blank\">http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20201020/__2020102019234392773.mp4</a>"},{"pid":"f2b692f6ebdb74ae66f4bc41d76b3735ea9ed3db","tid":2256174,"uid":10337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e05ca4b8e2adf69119daa5440851a4e6dc0bd6b0","tid":2256174,"uid":50041,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T07:05:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20201020/__2020102019234392773.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20201020%2F__2020102019234392773.mp4&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLKf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=f924d5c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20201020%2F__2020102019234392773.mp4&h=eda4b4f9\" target=\"_blank\">http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20201020/__2020102019234392773.mp4</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T07:07:53.000Z","msg":"就係睇完呢條片 先醒返起<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73fb58f883ee25bc0e0f35a84890a7372265ea93","tid":2256174,"uid":32380,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T07:09:42.000Z","msg":"睇圖係有空翻，文字又冇<br />\n咁究竟有定冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"h